Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Fully fitted with furniture and offices

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Modern two level building located in the vibrant Northbridge cultural precinct.

5 minute walk to Perth Central Station, with an abundance of food and beverage amenity nearby.

The offices are modern and bright and include a high quality fitout.

- Large boardroom
- 9 offices
- 2 meeting rooms
- 32 open plan workstations
- large kitchen and staff area

Flexible and highly competitive lease terms.

Area - 656sqm
Asking rent $350/sqm + incentives
Outgoings: $
Car bays: 6 secure undercover bays at $275 pcm.

The property comprises a self-contained office tenancy of 56sqm, occupying a ground floor position within a modern mixed use development. 

The ground floor tenancy boasts excellent natural light and is currently configured with a boardroom, open plan area, kitchenette and bathroom facilities. The complex provides allocated undercover secure car parking.

The building is well located with great exposure onto Newcastle Street and in close proximity to the CBD, providing good access to the main arterial roads.

Availability: Immediately.

For further information, or to arrange an inspection, please contact the appointed agent

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Near Perth City Link & train station

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
This 1st floor approx. 370sqm tenancy sitting on the corner of Roe Street, the Queen Street extension and Nicks Lane (entrance to Chinatown) is ideally positioned to benefit from the Perth City Link, Perth Arena and train/bus port.   

With views overlooking the Perth CBD and Tenant adjacencies that include; Pleased To Meet You, Sneaky Tonys, the Standard as well as the ever-popular Billy Lees.  

Just a short stroll from William Street, James Street (with all of its late night favourites), and the new DoubleTree Hotel by the Hilton Group. 

This absolutely prime Bar/Restaurant opportunity will not last long.

Situate your business on William Street within Perth's vibrant city-fringe destination.

The first floor walk-up offices are situated directly above a top tier architectual firm and provide direct street access with fantastic signage and exposure. Internally the offices provide excellent natural light with full height glazing and operable windows.

The tenancy comprises two large open plan areas, large boardroom, 2 meeting rooms, staff breakout area and male and female amenities. 

Buildings of this quality with on-site parking are a rarity in this exciting inner-city location.  This is a unique opportunity for a company to move into a freestandng building on the fringe of the Perth CBD with outstanding nearby amenities and culture on the doorstop.

Level 1: 335sqm
Asking Rent: $325/sqm
Estimated Outgoings: $76/sqm for the 20/21 financial year.
Car Bays: 5 secure car bays available @ $200 per bay per month.
